library(tidyverse)
library(CodeClanData)
library(tidyr)
revenue <- qb_revenue_breakdown
sales <- qb_monthly_sales
competitors <- qb_competitors
devices <- qb_device_data

#q1

revenue %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = Year,
         y = Revenue,
         fill = Product))+
  geom_col()+
  labs(title = "Annual Revenue Breakdown by Product")

#q2

kwikbit_sales <- sales %>% 
  filter(Cashflow == "Kwikbit Unit 1 Sales",
         Date >= "2019-01-01")

kwikbit_sales %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = Date,
             y = Amount))+
  geom_line()

#q3

cost_rev <- qb_monthly_sales %>% 
  filter(Cashflow != "Kwikbit Unit 1 Sales")

cost_rev %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = Date,
             y = Amount,
             colour = Cashflow))+
  geom_line()

#q4

competitors %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = Year,
             y = Revenue,
             group = Company,
             fill = Company))+
  geom_area()

#q5

competitors %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = Year,
             y = Revenue,
             group = Company,
             colour = Company))+
  geom_line()+
  geom_point()

#q6
